  "seeder_contract": [
    "ThemePresetSeeder runs on module boot and inserts every preset above with tenant_id=NULL.",
    "For presets that declare tokens_deltas_from_<other-preset>: the seeder resolves the base preset's tokens map, merges the deltas on top, and writes the fully-materialised tokens jsonb — the theme_presets table row NEVER carries a delta reference. Every stored preset is a complete token map.",
    "Seeder is idempotent — reruns update existing rows by slug rather than duplicating. See ThemePresetSeeder for the exact upsert semantics.",
    "Adding a new platform preset requires: (1) new entry here, (2) PATCH via platform-admin API after deploy OR a data migration that inserts the row alongside the code deploy."
  ]
